  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2009-03-05",
    "date": "2009-03-25T15:31:18Z",
    "text": "COLA Fairness Act of 2009 - Requires the Bureau of Labor Statistics of the Department of Labor to establish: (1) a mapping of the United States comprising 14 specified regions; and (2) particular monthly consumer price indices for such regions for computation of cost-of-living increases for Social Security and Medicare (title XVIII of the Social Security Act) benefits."
